original_title: Found Footage Festival Volume 6: Live in Chicago
overview: In their most unsettling compilation to date, Found Footage Festival curators Joe Pickett and Nick Prueher present their latest and greatest array of VHS wonders. Didgeridoos will be blown, sponges will be rainbowed, opossums will be massaged, and senior citizens will be fed salad. It's all here! Recorded live at the Music Box Theatre in Chicago.
tagline: An Explosive Collection of Odd & Hilarious Found Videos
title: Found Footage Festival Volume 6: Live in Chicago
